metadata.description: This is the first design of the Brand. This was made at the time when black people were protesting in the USA. With the face looking at the front and at the same time, looking sideways, We look at each other, Our personalities are torn in Identities, for skin color, for religion, for countries, for political parties, for sex. That Black, White, and brown are all colors and colors do not define us as human beings.
metadata.name: MythsnMaths #1
